READY PLAYER ONE (2018)
Lot #285 - Wade Watts' (Tye Sheridan) Production-Made VR Goggles
? Login to See Winning Bid
Estimate: $5,000 - $10,000
Get Shipping Quote
  • Our experts notes

    Bidding for this lot will end on Tuesday, March 12th. The auction will begin at 9:00AM PDT and lots are sold sequentially via live auctioneer; tune in to the live streaming broadcast on auction day to follow the pace. Note other lots in the auction may close on Wednesday, March 13th or Thursday, March 14th.

    Wade Watts' (Tye Sheridan) VR goggles from the production of Steven Spielberg's Ready Player One. Wade wore his dodgier goggles at the beginning of the film when he entered the OASIS, before later upgrading to a more advanced pair. Adapted from Ernest Cline's hit book, the film was Academy Award-nominated for its visual effects.

    These resin goggles with a semi-transparent acrylic visor, elasticized strap, and foam padding were created for the production but ultimately unused in the final cut. They are decorated with various stickers related to films and video games. It is designed to appear well used and exhibits some additional wear from production use. Dimensions: 3.5" x 6.5" x 2" (9 cm x 16.5 cm x 5 cm)

    Estimate: $5,000 - 10,000
